version_description:
The new 1.7707 version is live! This updates contains the following changes:
- The Grand Prix has been fixed! Time to challenge other players to races!
- Improved stability during in app purchases.
- Minor bugfixes.

- Improvement on Grand Prix Matchmaking
- Fix on facebook link

- Christmas has come to Motor World, and your workers have put up surprise decorations!
- The Grand Prix returns!
- Rewarded videos (for Mystery Cards) are back!
- Bug fixes: in particular one causing loss of small amounts of progress between logins.

"- Valentines day is here, with fantastic Special Offers and a shiny new Game Icon
- Fixed Bug where event Rewards were not received properly
- Minor Bug Fixes"

- Fix on Local notification
- Fix on Breeding Cost

Get Ready for St Patrick's Day!
Enjoy a greener factory and exclusive new content for St Patrick's Day!
This update also fixes minor issues.
Get in the Easter mood! New splash screen, icon and exclusive offers are incoming! This update also fixes minor issues.
Minor bug fix

Improved stability
Minor bug fix
12 new languages (Japanese, Korean, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Russian, Portuguese, Netherlands, Indonesian, Arabic, Turkish, Thai, Vietnamese)
Minor bug fix
Summer is finally here, discover exclusive offers and events in this brand new update!

HAPPY BIRTHDAY!! Motor World: Car Factory celebrates its 5th Anniversary with this new update!
This update includes:
* 11 new exclusive Event cars!
* 2 new live Events with amazing prizes!
* Several bug fixes!

*Various Bug Fixes
*Game performance greatly improved again!

Bug fixes
Game performances improved
Various bug fix

Winter is coming.
Come and check our new version!
We wish you a Merry Christmas

- Bugs fixes
- Christmas Content removed

Thanks for playing! Ready to race?

So many cars to love, come and play now!
This version includes some bugs fixes and game performance improvements.

Several bugs have been fixed.
Thanks for your support, may the road be with you!

Friends codes are fixed!! They might be a bit longer, but you'll get your referral rewards!!
Plus, some other minor bugs have been fixed.
Thanks for your support!

The new update is live!
- Events are better than ever: nothing can stop you from getting amazing rewards!
- Game performance improved: harder, better, faster, stronger game experience!
- And many other issues fixed!

New Update!! The new version contains:
- Event rewards have been fixed!
- Connexion issues on some devices have been solved!
- Updated data protection and privacy policies.
- And much more!
